item.title: CVE-2021-41544|2024-08-04T03:15:29.195Z -- siemens -- siemens%20software%20center
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Siemens Software Center (All versions < V3.0). A DLL Hijacking vulnerability could allow a local attacker to execute code with elevated privileges by placing a malicious DLL in one of the directories on the DLL search path.
